## Memory Utilization in EC2 Instances

When we are launching EC2 Instances we will be scpecifying amoun of memory (RAM).To monitor the memory utilization by EC2 Instances we use aws cloudwatch
monitoring service which will collect various metrics from EC2 Instances.We can view those metrics in AWS cloudwatch console or through cloudwath API.
OS allocates RAM to applications and decides based on the situation.
